1Ô∏è‚É£ AWS Global Infrastructure 
       Region ‚Üí Geographic area (e.g., eu-west-1)
       Availability Zone (AZ) ‚Üí One or more data centers in a Region
       Edge Location ‚Üí Used for CDN (CloudFront, Global Accelerator)
       High availability = Multi-AZ
       Disaster recovery = Multi-Region

2Ô∏è‚É£ Shared Responsibility Model (Critical)
       1.AWS = Security of the Cloud
           -Physical hardware
           -Networking infrastructure
           -Hypervisor
           -Managed service patching (RDS engine, etc.)
       2.Customer = Security in the Cloud
           -IAM policies
           -Data encryption settings
           -Guest OS patching (EC2)
           -Security groups
       If it's EC2 ‚Üí YOU patch OS
       If it's RDS ‚Üí AWS patches engine
3Ô∏è‚É£ Core Compute Services
       | Service           | When Used                       |
       | ----------------- | ------------------------------- |
       | EC2               | Virtual servers                 |
       | Lambda            | Serverless event-driven compute |
       | ECS               | Containers                      |
       | Fargate           | Serverless containers           |
       | Elastic Beanstalk | PaaS deployment                 |
       | Auto Scaling      | Adjust capacity automatically   |
       
       Elasticity = Scale up/down
       Scalability = Handle growth
4Ô∏è‚É£ Storage 
       | Storage Type | Used For             |
       | ------------ | -------------------- |
       | S3           | Object storage       |
       | EBS          | Block storage (EC2)  |
       | EFS          | Linux file storage   |
       | FSx          | Windows file systems |
       | Glacier      | Archive              |

       S3 Storage Classes:
          S3 Standard     ‚Üí Frequent access
          S3 Standard-IA  ‚Üí Infrequent
          One Zone-IA     ‚Üí Cheaper, single AZ
          Glacier Flexible ‚Üí Minutes to hours retrieval
          Deep Archive ‚Üí 12+ hours retrieval
          Intelligent-Tiering ‚Üí Automatic movement
      Exam trick:
          ‚ÄúAutomatic tiering‚Äù ‚Üí Intelligent-Tiering 
          
